1. *Prerano* sam se probudio jutros. (I woke up *too early* this morning.)
2. Što je stigao *prerano*, morat ćemo ga malo pričekati. (Since he arrived *early*, we'll have to wait for him a bit.)
3. Rekao je da je još *prerano* za odlazak na spavanje. (He said it was still *too early* to go to bed.)
4. Nisam htjela da se *prerano* probudim, pa sam ugasila alarm. (I didn't want to wake up *too early*, so I turned off the alarm.)
5. *Preran* je bio odlazak mojih prijatelja, nedostajat će mi. (Their departure was *early*, I'll miss them.)
6. Nadam se da nije *prerano* za razgovor o našoj vezi. (I hope it's not *too early* to talk about our relationship.)
7. *Prerano* se radovao proljeću, kad je opet počela kiša. (He was looking forward to spring *too early*, when it started raining again.)
8. Ako se *prerano* javimo, možda nećemo uspjeti dobiti karte. (If we contact them *too early*, we might not be able to get tickets.)